refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraygnupg_import resourceidentifier stringkeydata
Iports the key keydata and returns an array with informations about the importprocess.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


  On success, this function returns and info-array about the importprocess.
  On failure, this function returns &false;.

  &reftitle.examples;



    procedural gnupg_import example


<?php
$res = gnupg_init();
$info = gnupg_import($res,$keydata);
print_r($info);
?>




     OO gnupg_import example


<?php
$gpg = new gnupg();
$info = $gpg -> import($keydata);
print_r($info);
?>
